    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "rebuilding sounds like a fairy tale. i've spent my whole life working toward this, and it's just... gone. every time i close my eyes i just see the looks on their faces. the disappointment is going to be unbearable. it feels like the only way to actually stop the noise and the shame is to just not be around to experience it anymore. is there even a point to fighting something that's already lost?",
